classes.description:
Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
See [CSS API](#css) below for more details.

descriptions.root: Styles applied to the root element.
descriptions.alignLeft: Styles applied to the root element if `align="left"`.
descriptions.alignRight: Styles applied to the root element if `align="right"`.
descriptions.alignAlternate: Styles applied to the root element if `align="alternate"`.
descriptions.missingOppositeContent: Styles applied to the root element if no there isn't TimelineOppositeContent provided.
descriptions.content: Styles applied to the timeline content node.
descriptions.oppositeContent: Styles applied to the timeline opposite content node.
